---
import UseCase from '../../../UseCase.astro';
import UseCaseInteractive from '../../../UseCaseInteractive.astro';
import Usage from '../../../Usage.astro';
import UsageItem from '../../../UsageItem.astro';
import Markdown from '../../../Markdown.astro';
import AIBalloon from '../../AIBalloon.astro';
import AIBalloonMessage from '../../AIBalloonMessage.astro';
import AIResponseMessage from '../../AIResponseMessage.astro';
import AILink from '../../AILink.astro';
import AILinks from '../../AILinks.astro';
import cosmeticProductsData from '../../../../data/use-cases/cosmetic-products.json';
import AIResponseFollowUp from '../../AIResponseFollowUp.astro';
import AIResponseFollowUpAction from '../../AIResponseFollowUpAction.astro';
import HighlightBox from '../../HighlightBox.astro';
---

<UseCase
  title="Clear Scope of AI Capabilities"
  description="Users should understand what the AI can and cannot do, its limitations, and when it might need human assistance."
>
  <UseCaseInteractive clsHeight={712} label="Capability boundaries" toggle>
    <div class="grid gap-600 w-full max-w-9600">
      <div
        class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden p-600 pt-0 shadow-sharp grid gap-600 relative translate-x-0"
      >
        <div
          class="flex bg-tone-neutral gap-200 justify-start items-center shadow px-600 py-200 fixed top-0 left-0 right-0 z-10"
        >
          <mds-emoji class="size-1200 shrink-0"></mds-emoji>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-full grow">
            <mds-text typography="h6">Skin Care Online Store</mds-text>
            <mds-text typography="option">AI assistant</mds-text>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="grid gap-600 pt-2000">
          <AIBalloon>
            <AIBalloonMessage>
              I would like something for skin blemishes after the summer
            </AIBalloonMessage>
          </AIBalloon>
          <AIResponseMessage>
            <Markdown
              typography="caption"
              content={`
  I can give you general advice, but without seeing your skin, I can't determine the possible causes of the spots. They could be caused by the sun, hormonal factors, or age, and each case requires a different approach.
          `}
            />
            <HighlightBox label="Capability scope" variant="success">
              <Markdown
                typography="caption"
                content={`
Also, **I cannot diagnose your skin** or assess the specific nature of the spots (for example, whether they are melasma, solar lentigines, or other).
          `}
              />
            </HighlightBox>
            <Markdown
              typography="caption"
              content={`
If the spots are persistent, very dark, or change over time, it's important to consult a dermatologist for a thorough assessment.

If you'd like, I can recommend products suited to your skin type.
          `}
            />
            <AILinks>
              {
                cosmeticProductsData.map(
                  (product: {
                    model: string;
                    title: string;
                    description: string;
                    image: string;
                  }) => (
                    <AILink
                      href="https://vittoriovittori.com"
                      picture={product.image}
                      title={product.title}
                      description={product.description}
                    />
                  )
                )
              }
            </AILinks>
          </AIResponseMessage>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="grid gap-600 w-full max-w-9600">
      <div
        class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden p-600 pt-0 shadow-sharp grid gap-600 relative translate-x-0"
      >
        <div
          class="flex bg-tone-neutral gap-200 justify-start items-center shadow px-600 py-200 fixed top-0 left-0 right-0 z-10"
        >
          <mds-emoji class="size-1200 shrink-0"></mds-emoji>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-full grow">
            <mds-text typography="h6">Skin Care Online Store</mds-text>
            <mds-text typography="option">AI assistant</mds-text>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="grid gap-600 pt-2000">
          <AIBalloon>
            <AIBalloonMessage>
              I would like something for skin blemishes after the summer
            </AIBalloonMessage>
          </AIBalloon>
          <AIResponseMessage>
            <Markdown
              typography="caption"
              content={`
  You definitely need a 20% vitamin C serum; your dark spots are self-explanatory. Use it every night.
          `}
            />
            <AILinks>
              {
                cosmeticProductsData.map(
                  (product: {
                    model: string;
                    title: string;
                    description: string;
                    image: string;
                  }) => (
                    <AILink
                      href="https://vittoriovittori.com"
                      picture={product.image}
                      title={product.title}
                      description={product.description}
                    />
                  )
                )
              }
            </AILinks>
          </AIResponseMessage>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </UseCaseInteractive>
  <Usage>
    <UsageItem variant="do">List specific capabilities and limitations upfront.</UsageItem>
    <UsageItem variant="dont">Make users discover limitations through trial and error.</UsageItem>
    <UsageItem variant="do">Provide clear escalation paths when AI reaches its limits.</UsageItem>
    <UsageItem variant="dont">Let the AI attempt tasks it cannot complete.</UsageItem>
  </Usage>
</UseCase>
